; Tohoku Region
* [[Aomori Prefecture]]: [[Hirosaki]] - Nishishigemori area ({{ill|Zenrin Street|ja|禅林街|12=draft|12=draft}}), {{ill|Niideramachi|ja|新寺町 (弘前市)|12=draft|12=draft}} area
