; Tohoku Region
* [[Aomori Prefecture]]: [[Hirosaki]] - Nishishigemori area ({{ill|Zenrin Street|ja|禅林街|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zenrin Street|qq=}}), {{ill|Niideramachi|ja|新寺町 (弘前市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Niideramachi|qq=}} area
